title: 820-00239 - No image, turns on and hear sound - small liquid damage
message:
820-00239

had small liquid damage at U8501, so i replaced U8501, U8510,  U8500, did not work so i also replaced U8400, 

i tried a new display, and still nothing, 

it this helps any, the SMC had some damage coming from around PIN 161 (PM_SLP_S3_L)

PM_SLP_S3_L is present by the way 3.3V
